Tue Aug  6 17:56:40 2013  Koichi Sasada  <ko1@atdot.net>

	* vm_insnhelper.c (vm_push_frame): change type of stack_max to size_t.

Tue Aug  6 17:42:47 2013  Nobuyoshi Nakada  <nobu@ruby-lang.org>

