Mon Jun  3 23:11:19 2013  Ayumu AIZAWA  <ayumu.aizawa@gmail.com>

	* lib/fileutils.rb: fix behavior when mkdir/mkdir_p accepted "/".
	* test/fileutils/test_fileutils.rb: add test for above change.
